popularityCurve.label: here you'll find new england charm on the shores of lake erie and the vermilion river lighthouse and sailboat enthusiasts will be right at home stores shops and the inland seas maritime museum remind you of decades past during the summer months you can hear concerts and sample hand dipped ice cream cones in the town square don't forget to visit thomas edison's birthplace in milan just a few miles away
